"Zaporozhian Cossacks to the Turkish Sultan!

O sultan, Turkish devil and damned devil's kith and kin, secretary to Lucifer himself. What the devil kind of knight are thou, that canst not slay a hedgehog with your naked arse? The devil shits, and your army eats. Thou shalt not, thou son of a whore, make subjects of Christian sons; we have no fear of your army, by land and by sea we will battle with thee, fuck thy mother.

Thou Babylonian scullion, Macedonian wheelwright, brewer of Jerusalem, goat-fucker of Alexandria, swineherd of Greater and Lesser Egypt, pig of Armenia, Podolian thief, catamite of Tartary, hangman of Kamyanets, and fool of all the world and underworld, an idiot before God, grandson of the Serpent, and the crick in our dick. Pig's snout, mare's arse, slaughterhouse cur, unchristened brow, screw thine own mother!

So the Zaporozhians declare, you lowlife. You won't even be herding pigs for the Christians. Now we'll conclude, for we don't know the date and don't own a calendar; the moon's in the sky, the year with the Lord, the day's the same over here as it is over there; for this kiss our arse!"

Anauê! 85 YEARS OF THE FIRST AND ONLY ONE BRAZILIAN IDEOLOGY!

On October 9th, 2017, it will have been 110 years since the birth of Horst Wessel, the greatest martyr of the National Socialist movement. I hope that all the youth of the world will one day praise that young boy for the life he had given, never once backing down from his convictions, only ever escalating the efforts he put forth so that Germany may flourish under the banners of the swastika. Navigating the political anarchy of the time, Wessel found himself in a number of different bands of men who had right wing convictions but it was the Sturmabteilung that would steal his heart and the communists that would steal him away from us. In doing so the red scum gave the National Socialists of Germany a means to awaken the spirit of the volk. They had brutally stolen away the life of a son, a young man at the age of 22 Horst Wessel lay bleeding at the front door of his own apartment. The blood of the greatest martyr was not spilled in vain though, his radical actions and mindset had brought him far in life and in death, as so often is the case, the boy became a legend.

Goebbels made certain that the legacy of the young Wessel would not be forgotten and he and his comrades of the National Socialist movement paid tribute to Wessel with a large burial procession, documented and used as an inspirational piece of propaganda to awaken the anger of the people and commit the idea of ultimate sacrifice into the minds of Wessel’s still living brothers in brown.

Of course, one could ramble on about the many things Wessel achieved in his short life, but I believe it is more important to pose a question. Where will you be at the age of 22? Will you be so feared by your opposition that they feel it necessary to resort to physical violence? Will you be so radical as to march alongside your brothers against all odds, looking death in the eye without blinking? Are you, today, willing to pay the ultimate price for the freedom of your people? Freedom from this JEWISH TYRANNY?

If you answered yes to all of the above you carry the spirit of Wessel in you, as all young Fascist MUST in these trying times. The Kali Yuga is around you, strengthen yourself and use the martyr’s death as a guiding light so that you may heal the world in the cleansing fires of Fascism. Perhaps one day it will be YOUR name which strikes fear into the enemy. YOUR name which will be remembered by your comrades. YOUR name which will inspire a new generation of dedicated youthful men seeking to take back what is rightfully theirs.

Hail Wessel! You will NEVER be forgotten!
